• Phát triển mối quan hệ gắn kết giữa PACE và các khách hàng/ doanh nghiệp mà mình phụ trách.

Branding Executive will play a key role in promoting GHTK’s brand to the community, as well as positioning this brand in customers’ mind in a clear and thorough way, contributing to the comprehensive development of the company

RESPONSIBILITY
- Establish and develop strategic plan to position/bring GHTK’s brand to target customers, which are online business units;
- Research and implement activities in accordance with the brand development strategy to maximize GHTK image and properly convey the message and values of GHTK to target customer groups;
- Manage GHTK’s brand identity system on all communication channels;
- Coordinate with Communication and Marketing Department to conduct and optimize brand promotion activities to create consistency and impression.

